{"tid":33173,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做人好多煩惱好辛苦","createTime":"2016-12-10T15:46:02.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T16:59:24.000Z","uid":24747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4286b676f734bd957445a598773d5613f432cde4","tid":33173,"uid":24747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:46:02.000Z","msg":"人愈大 發現好多野都變左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細細個可以自娛 好開心好易咁過一日<br />\n到宜家大個 發現身邊既朋友一個一個咁小 <br />\n大個左 有好多野發現埋唔到冷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時真係覺得好無謂 點解要有咁多有刺既說話<br />\n唔通連凡事留一線 日後好相見咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到其他朋友冇呢個情況出現 都真係有小小葡萄<br />\n唔知有冇巴打同我一樣都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：sorry for 長文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f26fb535f3c30d3721fa61d4ded94bd0ae22e29","tid":33173,"uid":8028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:56:14.000Z","msg":"我無朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c4a4f3a00793e48a6e825752d0718407679886e","tid":33173,"uid":24747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T16:59:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我無朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你又係慘小小既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}